snippet.title: Super Chuck Norris Bros. Teaser
snippet.description:
I really need to update my videos more often. To clear up the misunderstandings, the game was cancelled years ago. I lost interest in its development, that and the original closed format (editable) file not only doesn't work anymore but its lost. You can still download the beta game. I should've just posted this direct link ages ago:

Super Chuck Norris Bros Demo
http://www.box.net/public/yp6t8uvu0u
